# Components List

## Hardware Components

| Component | Quantity | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| BME280 Sensor | 6 | Temperature, humidity and pressure monitoring |
| DS3231 RTC Module | 1 | Time-stamp data logging |
| 3V Coin Vibration Motor | 6 | Micro-vibrations for blood circulation |
| SG90 Servo Motor | 2 | Lateral bed movement simulation |
| ESP32 Dev Board | 1 | Central control unit |
| 7.4V 2S LiPo Battery (3000mAh) | 1 | Main power source |
| LM2596 Buck Converter | 1 | Voltage conversion 7.4V → 5V |
| AMS1117 3.3V LDO Regulator | 1 | Voltage conversion 5V → 3.3V |
| TP4056 LiPo Charger Module | 2 | Battery charging |
| MicroSD Card Module (SPI) | 1 | Data storage interface |
| MicroSD Card (8GB+) | 1 | Sensor data storage |
| TCA9548A I2C Multiplexer | 1 | Multiple BME280 sensor management |
| IRF520N MOSFET | 6 | Vibration motor control |
| 5A Fuse | 1 | Overcurrent protection |

## Key Components by Function

**Sensors:**
- 6x BME280 - Pressure, temperature, humidity monitoring
- 1x DS3231 RTC - Real-time clock for data timestamps

**Actuators:**
- 6x Vibration Motors - Blood circulation enhancement
- 2x Servo Motors - Automated bed repositioning

**Control & Power:**
- 1x ESP32 - Main microcontroller
- 1x LiPo Battery - Portable power source
- Power regulation circuits for voltage conversion

**Data Storage:**
- 1x MicroSD module + card - Sensor data logging

**Total Components:** 28 individual parts
